metadata.name: Zooties-Club33 Executive producer #1/50
metadata.description: This NFT will represent the holder is an executive producer in the instrumental track Zooties and entitled to a portion of all revenue generated by track.  Holders will have a say in future remixes,releases on instrumental with vocalists, art, and direction of track more details on executive producer token will come after all tracks claimed, as well as a free merch drop. There will be a total of 150 total minted in a total of 3 waves, each wave sell out will unlock a new announcement and another 50 added.
